EN: Bodyguards need to have good communication and coordination skills.

ZH: 在某些重要场合，政府会派遣保镖为高级官员提供安全保护。
EN: In certain important occasions, the government will dispatch bodyguards to provide security protection for senior officials.

ZH: 那位明星的保镖手持着一个黑色的行李箱，里面装满了他的私人物品。
EN: The bodyguard of that celebrity is holding a black suitcase filled with his personal belongings.
